<% content_for :title, "Programme confirmed" %>

<div class="govuk-grid-row">
    <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">

        <%= govuk_panel(
        title_text: "You’ve submitted your training information",
        text: "Academic year #{@induction_choice_form.cohort.start_year} to #{@induction_choice_form.cohort.start_year + 1}",
        classes: "govuk-!-margin-bottom-7") %>

        <%- if school_cohort.school_chose_fip? -%>
        <h2 class="govuk-heading-m">What to do next</h2>

        <p class="govuk-body">You need to:</p>
        <ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet">
            <li>choose one of the 6 DfE-funded training providers as soon as possible</li>
            <li>tell us each ECT and mentor’s name and email address as soon as possible</li>
            <li>have an appropriate body in place</li>
        </ul>

        <p class="govuk-body"><%= govuk_link_to "Read our guidance (opens in new tab)", step_by_step_path, target: "_blank" %> to find out how to complete these steps.</p>
        <p class="govuk-body">You do not need to let the DfE know which provider you choose. Your training provider will contact us to arrange funding.</p>

        <p class="govuk-link govuk-!-margin-top-7">
            <%= govuk_link_to("Continue to manage your training", schools_dashboard_path)  %>
        </p>

        <%- elsif school_cohort.school_chose_cip? -%>
        <h2 class="govuk-heading-m">What to do next</h2>

        <p class="govuk-body">You need to:</p>
        <ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet">
            <li>compare and choose which DfE-accredited materials you want to use</li>
            <li>use this service to tell us which materials you want to use</li>
            <li>tell us each ECT and mentor’s name and email address as soon as possible</li>
            <li>have an appropriate body in place</li>
        </ul>

        <p class="govuk-body">
            <%= govuk_link_to "Read our guidance (opens in new tab)", step_by_step_path, target: "_blank" %> to find out how to complete these steps.
        </p>

        <p class="govuk-link govuk-!-margin-top-7">
            <%= govuk_link_to("Continue to manage your training", schools_dashboard_path)  %>
        </p>

        <%- elsif school_cohort.design_our_own? -%>
        <h2 class="govuk-heading-m">What to do next</h2>

        <p class="govuk-body">You need to:</p>
        <ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet">
            <li>design a 2-year programme of support and training that covers every ‘learn that’ and ‘learn how to’ statement in the <a  href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/early-career-framework" class="govuk-link" rel="noreferrer noopener" target="_blank">Early Career Framework (ECF) (opens in new tab)</a></li>
            <li>contact your appropriate body to find out what evidence is needed to demonstrate that your programme:
                <ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet">
                    <li>is based on the ECF</li>
                    <li>meets the statutory requirements</li>
                </ul>
            </li>
        </ul>

        <p class="govuk-body">You do not need to add information about your ECTs and mentors to this service.</p>

        <p class="govuk-body"><a class="govuk-link" href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/early-career-framework-reforms-overview/early-career-framework-reforms-overview#schools-designing-and-delivering-their-own-ecf-based-induction" rel="noreferrer noopener" target="_blank"> See our statutory guidance (open in new tab)</a> for information about funding, time off, and roles.</p>

        <%- elsif school_cohort.no_early_career_teachers? -%>
        <h2 class="govuk-heading-m">What to do next</h2>
        <p class="govuk-body">Your school will not receive any more messages about statutory inductions for ECTs until the next academic year.</p>
        <p class="govuk-body">If any ECTs do join your school this year, you need to use this service to let us know.</a></p>

        <%- elsif school_cohort.school_funded_fip? -%>
        <h2 class="govuk-heading-m">What to do next</h2>
        <p class="govuk-body">You need to <a class="govuk-link" href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/early-career-framework-reforms-overview/early-career-framework-reforms-overview#FPL"> make your own arrangements with a training provider</a>, approved by the DfE.</p>
        <p class="govuk-body">You do not need to add information about your ECTs and mentors to this service.</p>
        <p class="govuk-body">If you change your mind about how you want to run your training, <%= render MailToSupportComponent.new("contact us") %></p>

        <p class="govuk-link govuk-!-margin-top-7">
            <%= govuk_link_to("Continue to manage your training", schools_dashboard_path)  %>
        </p>

        <%- else -%>
        <ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet">
            <li>you do not need to use this service to set up your training programme</li>
            <li>you’ll need to make your own arrangements with a
                <a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/early-career-framework-reforms-overview/early-career-framework-reforms-overview#FPL"
                class="govuk-link"
                target="_blank"
                rel="noopener noreferrer">training provider
                </a>, approved by the DfE
            </li>
            <li>if you change your mind about how you want to run your training, contact:
            <%= render MailToSupportComponent.new %>
            </li>
        </ul>
        <%- end -%>

    </div>
</div>
